text: Kinto Sol is a hip-hop group from Irámuco, Guanajuato, México. The members are three brothers: DJ Payback García (Javier García), El Chivo (Eduardo García) and the leader of the group Skribe (Manuel García). ==Discography== ===Albums=== *Kinto Sol (1999) *Del Norte al Sur (2001) *Hecho En Mexico (2003) *La Sangre Nunca Muere (2005) *Los Hijos Del Maíz (2007) *15 Rayos (2007) *Cárcel De Sueños (2009) *El Ultimo Suspiro (2010) *Familia, Fe y Patria (2012) *La Tumba del Alma (2013) *Protegiendo el Penacho (2014) *Lo Que No Se Olvida (2015) *Somos Once (2017) *Lengua Universal (2018) Category:1990s Mexican music groups Category:2000s Mexican music groups Category:Mexican rap music groups Category:2010s music groups Category:Musical groups established in 1999 Category:Mexican musical groups Category:1990s establishments in Mexico
